blog.name: theplagerist
blog.title: Utimate Rebirth
blog.description: Ayo,Just a couple of some my sketches of my favorite spider-man series drawn by my favorite artist. One of my goals is to redraw some issues (112-133) from the series in his style just for fun. So expect at least a page a day and they’ll be some random pages or covers that I enjoyed from the series that I like. My main goal is that hopefully this blog catches the eye of some writer from Marvel that inspires them to bring back the ultimate marvel universe with the original Spider-Man. But we’ll see.

summary: This was the TOUGHEST and LONGEST sketch I did that came from the Death of Spider-Man storyline. I’m not used to drawing more...
caption: This was the TOUGHEST and LONGEST sketch I did that came from the Death of Spider-Man storyline. I’m not used to drawing more than two characters on a page (especially a hulking goblin), but the challenge was well worth the result. Inking and color edition may or may not come out because well its a lot. haha(Ultimate Spider-Man Vol. 2 Issue 160)
